        List<PersonalRequeueInfo> loadPersonalRequeueInfo(Connection con,
                                                int operatorId,
                                                String sender,
                                                boolean owner,
                                                Long emaildate,
                                                Integer limit,
                                                List<Integer> subprojectIdList,

                                                List<Integer> doctypenIDs,
                                                Integer selectedMode)
                                                  throws SQLException
        Gets requeue data to be shown on the dash board
        Parameters:
        con - connection of database
        operatorId - operator id of current operator
        sender - sender of mails that will be shown
        owner - true, if you want to show mails from owner subprojects
        emaildate - email date of mails that will be shown
        limit - limit of mails
        subprojectIdList - subproject ids of mails
        ownersubprojectId - owner subproject ids
        responsibility - responsibilities of the current operator
        languageIds - language ids of mails
        type - type of mails
        doctypenIDs - types of mails to show
        selectedMode - 0 if you want to show incoming mails or 1 for outgoing mails
        Returns:
        List of PersonalRequeueInfo
        Throws:
        SQLException
